      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and has been super dependable for all my daily errands and weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, well-cared for, and ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
