    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2008 Porsche Cayman S featuring the venerable 3.4L M97 flat-six power plant. This mid-engine masterpiece delivers linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, offering an engagement level rarely found in modern counterparts. The chassis remains taut, showcasing exceptional torsional rigidity and high-speed stability. Notable mechanical highlights include a recently serviced Air Oil Separator (AOS) and a cooling system refresh with a new water pump. The hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback, while the staggered 18-inch alloy wheels are shod in high-performance rubber for maximum lateral grip. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical health is robust, with a clear induction note and smooth rev-matching capabilities. A purist's specification for those who prioritize corner-exit traction and balanced weight distribution.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
