    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a few minor stone chips on the hood tell the story of its highway journeys. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features supple leather upholstery with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic component\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service record including a recent brake pad replacement and synthetic oil change. It handles beautifully with a firm, responsive suspension and crisp shifting. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine care, this is it.",
      "price": 35500.0,
